HEADWORD: Erodent
<hw>E*rod"ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>erodens</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>erodere</ets>. See
